Entering my angel year, 33 ✨

I can’t say that life has not tested my spirit, hurt my heart or affected my mind in ways I never believed I could overcome,

Or that it hasn’t become more challenging as the years go by and more layers unfold but 

I can say that at each corner I was given the power and light to move through with a force that always leads me to an even higher place

I am grateful for where I am, where I have been and where I will be. The darkness, the beauty, the love are all part of a recipe to embody my highest self and she is my dream girl 🤍

I hope we all move through life with the same energy we have on birthdays, celebrate yourself today and always!
Make them go through ᴸᴼⱽᴱ to reach you ❤️‍🔥

The light in me honors the light in you ✨

Here to remind you that you are 100% the product of your thoughts.

It is not what we have been through but how we grow through it that brings us to where we are today.

It is not our emotions that magnify our strengths and weaknesses but how we navigate through them and our ability to control how we react when something doesn’t go as planned.

So choose positive thoughts, choose to see the light in everything around you, choose to prevail despite the difficulties, choose a higher vibration because you are in control and what you think, will become.

#lawofattraction #lifebydesign

"Why do you go away? So that you can come back. So that you can see the place you came from with new eyes and extra colors. And the people there see you differently, too. Coming back to where you started is not the same as never leaving"

Travel is the greatest teacher.

It will expand your mind, awaken your consciousness, give you rich experiences and inspire your soul in ways you can never truly describe with words.

There is a certain kind of magic in being so far from a place of comfort and so deep into a new setting that you can never truly return to who you were before you left home.

A flame of adoration for life is ignited and once it’s lit there is no dimming it.

🤍

May all your delulu come trululu ✨

Delusion is the highest form of manifestation.

This form of manifestation embodies the universal laws of attraction, assumption and vibration.

The law of attraction connects us with the ability to create our reality. Whatever you focus on, grows.

The law of assumption encourages us to believe that which we wish to be true as if it is already ours and so it shall be.

The law of vibration magnifies that we can attract all that we desire so long as we are vibrationally aligned with those desires.

You take a risk by traveling and hoping that everything falls into place as it should because you believe that it will be.

You order online with no actual knowledge of what the product will be like because you have faith it will be a great fit for you.

You wake up at the same time every day without knowing if any obstacles might be thrown in front of you on your commute because you don’t expect your journey to go any other way.

Every day we make decisions based off faith, in a state of alignment because of our confidence that it will work out as it always has.

Why don’t we channel the same energy into believing the life we crave is already ours?

Why don’t we blindly move forward knowing that no force can come between something that has already been written?

Why don’t we fiercely embrace that we have every single thing within us that we need to reach that higher version of ourselves that we’re striving to become because we’re already them?

What does it hurt to believe in yourself without reservation, to believe that nothing is too good for you, to believe that all that is good in this world is your birthright?

Move as if you’re divinely guided, because you are. Vibrate high as if you’re living in the reality you created because you are.

Everything beautiful in this life isn’t on its way to you, it’s already yours 🤍

#lawofattraction #manifestation #lifebydesign #losangeles
